[normal]’
[normal] in narrowing the
[normal] gap for disadvantaged children
[normal] using the 
[normal]available
[normal]. She was not able to find any evidence to suggest that it does narrow the gap. Indeed her brief survey shows that some academies a
[normal]re limiting opportunities by reducing the proportion of children with SEN. 
